            Professional Catering for Every Business Need
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-brand-indigo/70 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            From small team meetings to large corporate events, we understand the unique requirements of business catering and deliver consistent, professional service every time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          
          <!-- Executive Meetings -->
          <Card variant="elevated">
            <div class="p-8 text-center">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-brand-amber/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                <Icon name="mdi:tie" class="w-10 h-10 text-brand-amber" />
              </div>
              
              <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-brand-indigo mb-4">Executive Meetings & Business Catering</h2>
              
              <p class="text-brand-indigo/70 mb-6">
                Professional presentation and service for C-suite meetings, board discussions, and client presentations.
              </p>
              
              <div class="space-y-2 text-left mb-6">
                <div class="flex items-center text-brand-indigo/80 text-sm">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-brand-amber rounded-full mr-3"></span>
                  <span>Boardroom-style plated service</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center text-brand-indigo/80 text-sm">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-brand-amber rounded-full mr-3"></span>
                  <span>Quiet, professional service staff</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center text-brand-indigo/80 text-sm">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-brand-amber rounded-full mr-3"></span>
                  <span>Flexible timing around agendas</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </Card>

          <!-- Team Lunches -->
          <Card variant="elevated">
            <div class="p-8 text-center">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-brand-amber/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                <Icon name="mdi:account-group" class="w-10 h-10 text-brand-amber" />
              </div>
              
              <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-brand-indigo mb-4">Office Lunch Catering & Team Events</h2>
              
              <p class="text-brand-indigo/70 mb-6">
                Build team morale with delicious catered meals for staff meetings, training sessions, and team building events.
              </p>
              
              <div class="space-y-2 text-left mb-6">
                <div class="flex items-center text-brand-indigo/80 text-sm">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-brand-amber rounded-full mr-3"></span>
                  <span>Buffet-style for easy serving</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center text-brand-indigo/80 text-sm">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-brand-amber rounded-full mr-3"></span>
                  <span>Dietary accommodations included</span>
