          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center mt-12">
          <p class="text-white/70 text-sm mb-6">Need recurring catering? Ask about our corporate partnership program for preferred pricing and priority booking.</p>
          <a href="/start-planning" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-brand-amber text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-amber/90 transition-colors shadow-lg">
