            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-brand-indigo mb-2">Appetizers</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-1 text-brand-indigo/80 text-sm">
                  <li>• Thai spring rolls with sweet chili sauce</li>
                  <li>• Coconut chicken skewers</li>
                  <li>• Fresh vegetable crudité with herb dip</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-brand-indigo mb-2">Main Courses</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-1 text-brand-indigo/80 text-sm">
