              <p class="text-brand-indigo/60">Casual, delicious options for team gatherings</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-brand-indigo mb-2">Buffet Options</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-1 text-brand-indigo/80 text-sm">
                  <li>• Pad Thai station (chicken or tofu)</li>
                  <li>• Thai fried rice with vegetables</li>
